headline.main: With Economy Up, Crime Down, Why Are the Dutch Discontented?
headline.print_headline: With Economy Up, Crime Down, Why Are the Dutch Discontented?

lead_paragraph: The economy is up, unemployment is down and some Dutch prisons are so empty the government has been renting out cells.
